	<!-- Build Profiles guideline:
		Total 3 build profiles exist: main, batch, promo
		main: basic profile that adds all required projects (except batch and promo projects)
		batch: profile that adds batch project in addition to main
		promo: profile that adds promo project in addition to main
		batch and promo profiles are mutually exclusive (cannot co-exist in the same build)

		Build profile dependencies are declared within respective projects only: batch or promo
		To link either build or promo build dependencies one needs to import either
		spring/build/applicationContext-batch.xml
		or
		spring/build/applicationContext-promo.xml
		Any inner dependencies must be declared in some place that is being imported from either of these two configurations
		This said this particular file already imports one of the two configurations and this file needs not to be updated
		unless there is need to have changes in build profiles structure
